&#xD;
          -  Patient with a fracture of shoulder&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  With shoulder implant&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  With repetitive shoulder joint dislocation&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Unable to read and understand french&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  With psychiatric antecedents&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Patient deaf and hard-of-hearing&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Placed Under legal protection&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Pregnant women&#xD;
